<i>noun</i>: 한여름 [한녀름], 오뉴월 [오ː뉴월] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>한여름 [한녀름]</dt><br>
<dd>midsummer; middle of summer; the height of summer</dd><br>
<dd>더위가 가장 심할 무렵의 여름.</dd><br>
<dd>The time in summer when the heat is most severe.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>오뉴월 [오ː뉴월]</dt><br>
<dd>1. May and June; May or June</dd><br>
<dd>오월과 유월. 또는 오월이나 유월.</dd><br>
<dd>May and June, or May or June</dd><br>
<dd>2. midsummer; the peak of the summer</dd><br>
<dd>음력 오월과 유월에 해당하는 한여름.</dd><br>
<dd>The midsummer that falls in May and June in the Lunar calendar.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>